== 0.0.2 2010-02-22

* Fixed cosmetic mistakes
* Added .gitignore file
* Fixed problem with first empty line in all created files
* Removed background color for fields with errors
* Re-organized directories with CSS files
* Sidebar was improved and moved to plug-in. Now it is possible to choose actions of controller which will have sidebar in view.

